comment_data.body:
Please check the version of the Dart plugin you are using and post that here. The version that is reported is not expected to work with the version of IntelliJ you have. If this information is correct then I suggest you update your Dart plugin to 211.*.

I think this is a problem with the Dart plugin, not Flutter.

Without additional information we're unfortunately not sure how to resolve this issue. We're going to close this bug for now, but please don't hesitate to comment on the bug if you have any more information for us; we're happy to reopen. Thanks for your contribution!
